## `🚀 Featured Projects`

<table>
<tr>
<td width="50%" valign="top">

### 🛒 Retail Sales Intelligence Platform
End-to-end Azure data pipeline ingesting multi-source retail data, processing via Databricks + PySpark, and modeling a star-schema warehouse for Power BI dashboards tracking KPIs, inventory, and customer behaviour at scale.

**Stack:** `ADF` `Databricks` `PySpark` `Delta Lake` `Power BI`

[![View Project](https://img.shields.io/badge/View_Project-0078D4?style=flat-square&logo=github&logoColor=white)](PASTE_PROJECT_LINK)

</td>
<td width="50%" valign="top">

### 🔍 Financial Fraud Detection & Risk Monitoring
Real-time risk monitoring system using Spark Structured Streaming and ML models to flag anomalous transactions. Features automated alerting, audit trails, and an operational Power BI dashboard for compliance teams.

**Stack:** `PySpark` `Azure Databricks` `SQL` `Python` `Power BI`

[![View Project](https://img.shields.io/badge/View_Project-0078D4?style=flat-square&logo=github&logoColor=white)](PASTE_PROJECT_LINK)

</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="50%" valign="top">

### 🏥 AI Healthcare Recommendation Engine
Data platform unifying patient records, diagnostics, and treatment history to power an ML-based recommendation engine. Built with a medallion lakehouse architecture for data quality and governance.

**Stack:** `Python` `Azure Data Lake` `Databricks` `Delta Lake` `SQL`

[![View Project](https://img.shields.io/badge/View_Project-0078D4?style=flat-square&logo=github&logoColor=white)](PASTE_PROJECT_LINK)

</td>
<td width="50%" valign="top">

### 📈 Customer Analytics Dashboard
360° customer analytics solution consolidating CRM, transactional, and behavioural data into a single semantic model. Delivers cohort analysis, churn prediction inputs, and executive-level reporting via Power BI.

**Stack:** `ADF` `SQL` `Power BI` `Python` `Azure Synapse`

[![View Project](https://img.shields.io/badge/View_Project-0078D4?style=flat-square&logo=github&logoColor=white)](PASTE_PROJECT_LINK)

</td>
</tr>
